TI  - The Systematic Multi-domain Alzheimer's Risk Reduction Trial (SMARRT) intervention: A personalized approach to dementia risk reduction
PY  - 2024
T2  - Journal of Alzheimer's Disease
VL  - 102
IS  - 4
SP  - 1121
EP  - 1132
