TI  - Perceived Motivators, Barriers and Intervention Strategies Related to Weight Loss After Childbirth Among WIC Participants in Southern California
PY  - 2020
T2  - American Journal of Health Promotion
VL  - 34
IS  - 3
SP  - 294
EP  - 302
