AB  - Objective: To introduce status of studies about physical exercise in treating depression, and try to gives guidance of exercise rehabilitation to the depressive patients by means of exercise prescriptions. Data sources: Chinese articles about depression and exer cise published between January 1995 and December 2004 were searched in China journal full-text database by using the keywords of "depression, sport" in Chinese, relevant data were also searched manually.A computer-based online search of Medline database was undertaken to identify articles about depression and exercise published in English between January 1980 and December 2003, the keywords were "depression, sport". Study selection: The literatures were checked firstly. Inclusive criteria: investigative outcomes of physical exercise in treating depression, including horizontal and vertical epidemiological studies, experiments, clinical studies and Meta analysis. Data extraction: Total ly 28 articles were collected, 8 repetitive ones were excluded, and 20 were involved, including 2 revealed the adverse effect of depression, 5 about the horizontal and vertical epidemiological studies of physical exercise in treating depression, 1 was qualitative study, 2 were Meta analysis, 3 clinical studies and 8 were experimental studies. Data synthesis: Depression is one of the maj or mental-health problems in modern society which brings a lot of ill influences to our daily life. Many experimental and clinical studies have proved that physical exercise can effectively relieve depressive symptoms.In order to support that physical exercise can treat depression, it should be considered comprehensively from the pattern, intensity and lasting duration of exercise when establishing the exercise prescription, and then obtain the scientific and reasonable exercise prescription. Conclusion: Though it was discovered that physical exercise can case the depressive symptoms in the research of the laboratory, and decreased the occurrence rate of depression, For supporting better that the exercise can cure to depression, it must have something as the assurance of depression on the research, which included the experiment of the perfect design, fit tool of diagraph depression, stimulate through the sport that quantity turn and the other controlled latent factor which can influence depression. In addition, need the further research the depressions nerve physiology mechanism of depression and the effect of cure with exercises, must more confirm that the result of the exercise treatment depression from the clinic. Finally, demanded comprehensive consideration of aspects, just from sport method, sport strength and keep on the time, then got the sport prescription of a science reasonable.
